Package: qtkit
Title: Quantitative Text Kit
Version: 0.11.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jerid", "Francom", , "francojc@wfu.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5972-6330"))
Description: Support package for the textbook "An Introduction to
    Quantitative Text Analysis for Linguists: Reproducible Research using
    R" (Francom, 2024) <doi:10.4324/9781003393764> (available only after August 12, 2024). Includes functions to acquire,
    clean, and analyze text data as well as functions to document and share the
    results of text analysis. The package is designed to be used in conjunction with
    the book, but can also be used as a standalone package for text analysis.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://qtalr.github.io/qtkit/, https://github.com/qtalr/qtkit
